room_title: Escape room "The Time Machine" by Escape Room Lititz in Lancaster
room_description: Oops. Professor Wright, who usually isn’t, has done it again. It was supposed to be a quick trip in the time machine to the past, see some sights, then back to the workshop. You managed to get to the correct place, but the wrong time. You must get your time machine working again and back to the correct time in one hour. Otherwise… well, let’s not even consider what would happen if you failed.
